LAHORE, Apr 23 (APP): Prominent religious scholar of Jamia Naeemia Lahore, Mufti Raghib Hussain Naeemi on Sunday called on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif and appreciated his efforts to provide free atta to the poor people during the holy month of Ramazan ul Mubarak
During a meeting, Mufti Naeemi also extended Eid greetings, PM Office Media Wing said in a press release.
